    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A thin ray of destructive chakra springs from your pointing finger to a target that you can see within range. The target can be a creature or an object.</p><p>A creature targeted by this jutsu must make a Dexterity saving throw. On a failed save, the target takes 14d6 + 40 fire or lightning damage. If this damage reduces the target to 0 hit points, it is disintegrated.</p><p>A disintegrated creature and everything it is wearing and carrying, except chakra-enhanced items, are reduced to a pile of fine gray dust.</p><p>This jutsu automatically disintegrates a Large or smaller non-chakra-enhanced object. If the target is a Huge or larger object or creation of force, this jutsu disintegrates a 10-foot cube portion of it. A chakra-enhanced item is unaffected by this jutsu.</p><p></p>",
